import React, { Component } from 'react' import './skills.css' import Title from './Title'; import { DiHtml5, DiCss3, DiReact, DiJavascript, DiBootstrap, DiNodejs, DiFirebase, DiMongodb, DiGit, DiGithub} from "react-icons/di"; import ScrollAnimation from 'react-animate-on-scroll'; export default class Skills extends Component { render() { return (
<p className = "subtitles">Front-end</p> <span className ="skillIcon"> <i class="devicon-html5-plain-wordmark"></i> <i class="devicon-css3-plain-wordmark"></i> <i class="devicon-javascript-plain"></i> <i class="devicon-react-original-wordmark"></i> <i class="devicon-bootstrap-plain-wordmark"></i> </span> <p className = "subtitles">Server</p> <span className ="skillIcon"> <i class="devicon-nodejs-plain-wordmark"></i> <i class="devicon-express-original-wordmark"></i> </span> <p className = "subtitles">Database</p> <span className ="skillIcon"><DiFirebase/> <i class="devicon-mongodb-plain-wordmark"></i> </span> <p className = "subtitles">Testing</p> <span className ="skill">TDD/Jest</span> <p className = "subtitles">Metodologies It</p> <span className = "skill">Agile/Scrum/Kanban</span> <p className = "subtitles"> Tools</p> <span className ="skillIcon"> <i class="devicon-git-plain-wordmark"></i> <i class="devicon-github-plain-wordmark"></i> <i class="devicon-trello-plain-wordmark"></i> </span> <p className = "subtitles">Prototyping</p> <span className ="skill">Figma</span> </section> </ScrollAnimation> </React.Fragment> ) } }
